<i>It's another kind of weapon</i>

50:59.889 --> 51:04.492
and it is for unlimited range in a very high speed

51:04.893 --> 51:07.028
and in a very low signature.

51:07.030 --> 51:09.564
So this give you a huge opportunity...

51:10.666 --> 51:13.935
<i>And the superpowers have to change</i>

51:13.937 --> 51:16.003
<i>the way we think about warfare.</i>

51:18.241 --> 51:20.274
Finally we are transforming our military

51:20.276 --> 51:22.944
for a new kind of war that we're fighting now...

51:24.413 --> 51:25.846
