51:27.182 --> 51:29.283
<i>We have made our military better trained,</i>

51:29.285 --> 51:32.186
<i>better equipped, and better prepared</i>

51:32.188 --> 51:34.956
<i>to meet the threats facing America today</i>

51:34.958 --> 51:37.191
<i>and tomorrow and long in the future.</i>

51:40.963 --> 51:43.598
Sanger: <i>Back in the end of the Bush Administration,</i>

