52:39.955 --> 52:43.624
<i>And U.S. Cyber Command is located</i>

52:43.626 --> 52:47.495
<i>at Fort Meade in the same building as the NSA.</i>

52:51.700 --> 52:53.734
Col. Gary D. Brown: <i>I was deployed for a year</i>

