54:30.198 --> 54:32.133
<i>Cyber Command extends that capability</i>

54:32.135 --> 54:35.503
<i>by saying that they will then take responsibility to attack.</i>

54:36.972 --> 54:39.974
Hayden: <i>NSA has no legal authority to attack.</i>

54:39.976 --> 54:42.209
<i>It's never had it, I doubt that it ever will.</i>

54:42.711 --> 54:44.779
