01:05:43.771 --> 01:05:46.807
to develop an entire new class of weapons.

01:05:52.380 --> 01:05:55.115
Chien: <i>STUXnet wasn't just an evolution.</i>

01:05:55.117 --> 01:05:57.784
<i>It was really a revolution in the threat landscape.</i>

01:05:59.587 --> 01:06:02.556
<i>In the past, the vast majority of threats that we saw</i>

01:06:02.558 --> 01:06:04.558
<i>were always controlled by an operator somewhere.</i>

01:06:04.560 --> 01:06:06.259
