01:07:50.164 --> 01:07:53.300
<i>A double agent in Iran with access to Natanz,</i>

01:07:53.868 --> 01:07:55.602
<i>but I don't really know.</i>

01:07:55.604 --> 01:07:58.305
<i>What we had to focus on was to write the code</i>

01:07:58.906 --> 01:08:02.342
