01:09:06.308 --> 01:09:09.509
is controlled by another PLC,

01:09:09.511 --> 01:09:11.211
by another programmable logic controller.

01:09:13.413 --> 01:09:17.117
Chien: <i>STUXnet would wait for 13 days</i>

