were empty or at the beginning of the enrichment process.

01:09:31.799 --> 01:09:34.167
<i>What STUXnet did was it actually would sit there</i>

01:09:34.169 --> 01:09:36.870
<i>during the 13 days and basically record</i>

01:09:36.872 --> 01:09:38.872
<i>all of the normal activities</i>

01:09:38.874 --> 01:09:40.407
<i>that were happening and save it.</i>

