01:10:29.523 --> 01:10:32.058
Chien: <i>And at two hertz, sort of an opposite effect occurs.</i>

01:10:32.060 --> 01:10:34.327
<i>You can imagine a toy top that you spin</i>

01:10:34.329 --> 01:10:37.230
<i>and as the top begins to slow down, it begins to wobble.</i>

01:10:37.232 --> 01:10:39.232
<i>That's what would happen to these centrifuges.</i>

01:10:39.234 --> 01:10:41.267
<i>They'd begin to wobble and essentially shatter</i>

01:10:41.269 --> 01:10:42.502
<i>and fall apart.</i>

