01:10:52.714 --> 01:10:54.514
<i>So the computer's sitting there thinking,</i>

01:10:54.516 --> 01:10:56.216
<i>"yep, running at 1,000 hertz, everything is fine.</i>

01:10:56.218 --> 01:10:58.118
<i>Running at 1,000 hertz, everything is fine."</i>

01:10:58.120 --> 01:11:00.954
<i>But those centrifuges are potentially spinning up wildly,</i>

01:11:00.956 --> 01:11:02.756
<i>a huge noise would occur.</i>

