01:11:40.929 --> 01:11:42.495
<i>So you would have these operators</i>

01:11:42.497 --> 01:11:44.631
<i>slamming on that button over and over again</i>

01:11:44.633 --> 01:11:45.799
<i>and nothing would happen.</i>

01:11:47.101 --> 01:11:50.670
Yadlin: <i>If your cyber weapon is good enough,</i>

